u0027t use it again until you finish a long rest","level":1}],"id":"Custom0365bb53-aacd-43d2-a5d4-c72c2cdf9c1c","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Mantle of Flame","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":1},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"If you are reduced to 0 hit points, you can use your reaction instead be reduced to 1 hit point, and each creature within 10 feet of you takes fire damage equal to half your sorcerer level + your Charisma modifier.\n\nIf you use this feature while under the effects of your Mantle of Flame, this feature instead deals fire damage equal to your sorcerer level + double your Charisma modifier, and your Mantle of Flame immediately ends. Once you use this feature, you can\u0027t use it again until you finish a long rest","level":6}],"id":"Customc9c21303-0d6d-440a-8ead-367caeebecce","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Phoenix Spark","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":6},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"When you expend a spell slot to cast a spell that includes a fire damage roll, you regain hit points equal to the slot\u0027s level + your Charisma modifier","level":14}],"id":"Custom66987d86-2d54-4ab8-94bc-c24b4159329f","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Nourishing Fire","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":14},{"feat":{"descriptionModels":[{"description":"While under the effect of your Mantle of Flame feature, you gain additional benefits:\n\nYou have a flying speed of 40 feet and can hover.\nYou have resistance to all damage.\nIf you use your Phoenix Spark, that feature deals an extra 20 fire damage to each creature","level":18}],"id":"Custom52503a72-ac69-4fa0-95ba-e27ece4044b5","isFeature":true,"jsonType":"feat","level":1,"name":"Form of the Phoenix","notes":"","type":"Feat"},"level":18}],"hpModifier":"Constitution","id":"sorcerer_phoenix_sorcery","jsonType":"class","languages":[],"modelType":"Archetype","multiclassArmor":true,"multiclassSkills":true,"multiclassTools":